{"tid":2500173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"打mhr識到個女仔叫我砌佢","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T12:36:34.000Z","uid":193285,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ede0ca354fc164e20ea948ecbbf2f8414cc8b7b3","tid":2500173,"uid":193285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排因為動森熱潮嘅關係，應該好多女仔都買咗switch。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟本身玩過前作，所以有番啲底子，mhr推出嗰日即刻肝上hr7爆咗機（暫時）。由於初期遊戲內容太少，所以決定周圍救濟下新手，咁啱入咗個hr1玩家嘅大廳(睇id似係女仔嘅新手)，陪佢由hr1慢慢打上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打咗一陣之後發覺溝通唔係太方便，而且switch個打字系統太垃圾（任粉勿屌），打字詢問下得知對方有用開discord，就互add咗friend順便用埋voice chat方便交流。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個女仔嘅icon又pure又true，一開mic把聲勁溫柔，話從來未見過陌生男仔咁man，叫佢企埋一邊等攞報酬，對話中仲透露自己單身。<br />\n話雖如此，下位就話啫，上位啲怪高攻又多血，佢平時企喺山頂位觀戰就輕鬆，我喺下面都不知打得幾吃力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不經不覺我哋已經打到上位奇怪龍，我心諗咁樣唔掂，佢到上位任依然著住下位裝，又唔幫手落場打，咁樣玩嚟都冇癮啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就開mic話：不如教妳砌裝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n她突然回我話：我想你砌我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢句話嘅意思係想我幫佢測試下位防具嘅防禦力，抑或係佢知自己經常翹埋雙手食花生想我教訓佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我即刻二話不說用翔蟲飛上山頂，起手拔刀二連（係男人一定玩太刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）打咗佢兩下，再回佢：砌咗妳兩鑊，夠皮味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，我嗰兩下將佢打落山頂，跌咗喺奇怪龍隔離，瞬間被秒殺。佢無啦啦離開chat room，跟手block咗我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下大家我已經照做個女仔做咩block咗我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時下啲女仔真係奇怪過奇怪龍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daf9dc5d400a42b48d37fe5124608d5b9970f01","tid":2500173,"uid":364552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:16:37.000Z","msg":"Toxic"},{"pid":"ee4ec3911acef3063cd8a7e5610faa3d871d5e84","tid":2500173,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"冇甜0/10"},{"pid":"ef2c2aa17f753ff19681c8cbfddd7259aed917a9","tid":2500173,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:17:04.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"e905ce628a71eed56f1f26634f94e8d806a7c4ab","tid":2500173,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"0/10 作嚟都唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b960b89a163dee66e073577b15a86790bc049e","tid":2500173,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"0/10 作還作 唔加甜所以無分"},{"pid":"032e0a6dcd65830007b1f81328c88336a0a85090","tid":2500173,"uid":75870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"原來mhr整比弱智玩係真。。。"},{"pid":"f51d4e44ef71aa358642d6e0f74a3df9b296fa4b","tid":2500173,"uid":266892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"夠鐘食藥"},{"pid":"cc43bf9ae95de173ea21d385efe67bd460c867cd","tid":2500173,"uid":310423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"1/10<br />\n1分for表情應用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令文章更生動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f0dd03d93d4b10d87a3ab73a31713d8288fc0e","tid":2500173,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"On99/10"}]}